aller pressure,) we conclude that transmission spectroscopy is not the\noptimal science case to take advantage of the abilities offered by KMOS and\nVLT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Aug 2015 13:20:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-08-13"}
